org.springframework.web.accept

类 ParameterContentNegotiationStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.accept.MappingMediaTypeFileExtensionResolver
      • org.springframework.web.accept.AbstractMappingContentNegotiationStrategy
        • org.springframework.web.accept.ParameterContentNegotiationStrategy
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ContentNegotiationStrategy, MediaTypeFileExtensionResolver

    public class ParameterContentNegotiationStrategy
extends AbstractMappingContentNegotiationStrategy
    A ContentNegotiationStrategy that resolves a query parameter to a key to be used to look up a media type. The default parameter name is format.
    从以下版本开始:
    3.2
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
